<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Also there were plenty of issues he addressed in his report that were not addressed in his speech.27 issues I believe my number may be wrong. here is the outrage that he didn't address the other 27 issues?(or whatever the number is)<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
