So far it has been IRAQ that has ignored the UN.  Get things straight you Iraqi apologist. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=6094" target="top">Wenin Huirunda</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
